MERN Authentication System

## 📌 Project Description
This project is a MERN stack authentication system built using Node.js, Express.js, and MySQL. It provides secure user registration, login, JWT-based authentication, and dashboard CRUD operations.

---

## 🚀 Features

- User Registration with password hashing
- User Login with JWT authentication
- Forgot & Reset Password functionality
- Protected Routes using Middleware
- CRUD operations for items
- Dashboard statistics API

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MySQL
- JWT (jsonwebtoken)
- bcryptjs
- dotenv
- cors
- nodemailer

